data.value: Sri Dalada Maligawa or the Temple of the Sacred Tooth Relic is a Buddhist temple in the city of Kandy, Sri Lanka. The Sacred Tooth Relic of Lord Budhha is Kept here This is a most beautiful and a "must see" place in Sri Lanka..
